metadata.description:
Returning to the beginning of it all, this series fills in the blanks 
and tells the other story of what happened to Alice and her family on 
Calie's first trip into Wonderland. Struggling with a now shattered 
psyche, Alice must prevent the evil beings that inhabit that realm of 
madness from slipping into this world and infecting everyone she holds 
dear. But that's easier said than done as a mysterious entity is 
revealed to have been manipulating events from the very beginning.
metadata.name: Wonderland: Down the Rabbit Hole
